\f6\b\fs36 \cf4 1. Genesis 3: The Anatomy of the First Sin\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf4 To teach the Fall effectively, we have to look at 
\f6\b \cf4 \strokec4 how
\f0\b0 \cf4 \strokec4  the heart moved from trust to rebellion. It wasn't just about a piece of fruit; it was a shift in allegiance.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
